props.clippedLeft: Designates that the application’s [MNavigationDrawer](components/navigationDrawers) that is positioned on the left is below the `MAppBar`.
props.clippedRight: Designates that the application’s [MNavigationDrawer](components/navigationDrawers) that is positioned on the right is below the `MAppBar`.
props.collapseOnScroll: Puts the app-bar into a collapsed state when scrolling.
props.prominent: Increases the height of the toolbar content to 128px.
props.ScrollOffScreen: hrinks a prominent toolbar to a `Dense` or `Short` (default) one when scrolling.
props.short: Reduce the height of the toolbar content to 56px (112px when using the `Prominent` prop).
props.shrinkOnScroll: Shrinks a `Prominent` toolbar to a `Dense` or `Short` (default) one when scrolling.
props.value: Controls whether the component is visible or hidden.

contents.ExtensionContent: Slot positioned directly under the main content of the toolbar. Height of this slot can be set explicitly with the `ExtensionHeight` prop. If this slot has no content, the `Extended` prop may be used instead.
contents.ImgContent: Expects the [MImage](/components/images) component. Scoped props should be applied with @bind-value="props".
